{"tid":1176913,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"傳 Sony 明年將推出折疊屏幕手機 Xperia F，或支援 5G","createTime":"2019-05-29T13:28:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T19:11:03.000Z","uid":50534,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0e6e4d316a49c950968425a080b8dafdb68b10e6","tid":1176913,"uid":50534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T13:28:51.000Z","msg":"傳 Sony 明年將推出折疊屏幕手機 Xperia F，或支援 5g<br />\n傳 Sony 明年將推出折疊屏幕手機 Xperia F，或支援 5G<br />\n近日有網站指出 Sony 預計會在明年推出折疊屏幕手機，或命名為 Xperia F。根據爆料所指該機將會採用 Samsung OLED 柔性屏幕技術，屏幕比例或會是 Sony 近年力推的21:9 比例，而展開後屏幕比例則會變成 21:18，讓用戶可作平板電腦使用，同時預料該機會支援 5G 網絡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，Sony 在5月21日舉行 2019 財務年度企業戰略會議時表示 Sony Mobile 將會集中資源於日本、歐洲、台灣及香港等地，而澳洲、印度、加拿大、南美洲、非洲、中東地區等則被列入無關注或取消關注名單之一。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mobilemagazinehk.com/2019/05/xperiaf.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mobilemagazinehk.com%2F2019%2F05%2Fxperiaf.html&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1LhZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=b6154839\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mobilemagazinehk.com/2019/05/xperiaf.html</a>"},{"pid":"3bc166af8e00c5abe860c0dfb3809a40ddd2ad45","tid":1176913,"uid":83094,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T13:40:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7778fd372eb27c7599d98528503de50897f677c1","tid":1176913,"uid":41545,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T13:47:42.000Z","msg":"咪撚玩啦摺機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我Sony死忠都唔敢買呀"},{"pid":"ff41978c576f3b0088d78714d6b9d5b05dc512eb","tid":1176913,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T13:54:58.000Z","msg":"整返手提機先啦"},{"pid":"26ca9a7de5cf5cb4679f0c487687f329ca8f0ee6","tid":1176913,"uid":121697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T14:14:59.000Z","msg":"如果psv借屍還魂其實都ok"},{"pid":"24aa7732d2ee615e79f5066b2c87ec282ec9905a","tid":11